Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.71,TITLE @方正行楷_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\alpha20\frz-50\fs45\c&H858888&\pos(699,271)}请不要再依赖我了
